msgid "Dimensions"
msgstr "Dimensi"

msgid "Internal vs External Dimensions:"
msgstr "Dimensi Internal vs Eksternal:"

msgid ""
"• <strong>Internal dimensions</strong> are used for packing algorithm "
"calculations (determining what fits inside)"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Dimensi internal</strong> digunakan untuk perhitungan algoritma "
"pengemasan (menentukan apa yang masuk di dalamnya)"

msgid ""
"• <strong>Wall thickness</strong> defines the package material thickness "
"(default 0.5cm for standard cardboard)"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Ketebalan dinding</strong> menentukan ketebalan bahan kemasan "
"(default 0.5cm untuk karton standar)"

msgid ""
"• <strong>External dimensions</strong> are automatically calculated and sent "
"to shipping carriers for rate calculations"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Dimensi eksternal</strong> dihitung secara otomatis dan dikirim ke "
"penyedia pengiriman untuk perhitungan tarif"

msgid "Weight Constraints"
msgstr "Ketentuan Berat"

msgid "Weight values in kilograms"
msgstr "Nilai berat dalam kilogram"

msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi"

msgid ""
"Package cost and selection priority (higher = preferred for auto-packing)"
msgstr ""
"Biaya paket dan prioritas pemilihan (lebih tinggi = lebih disukai untuk "
"pengemasan otomatis)"

msgid "Dimensions (L×W×H)"
msgstr "Dimensi (P×L×T)"

msgid "Volume"
msgstr "Volume"

msgid "Enter dimensions to calculate volume"
msgstr "Masukkan dimensi untuk menghitung volume"

msgid "Calculated Volume (Internal)"
msgstr "Volume yang Dihitung (Internal)"

msgid "Enter dimensions and wall thickness to calculate external dimensions"
msgstr ""
"Masukkan dimensi dan ketebalan dinding untuk menghitung dimensi eksternal"

msgid "External Dimensions (for carriers)"
msgstr "Dimensi Eksternal (untuk penyedia pengiriman)"

msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Penggunaan"

msgid "Provider Information"
msgstr "Informasi Pemroses Pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Component and User cannot be changed after creation for security and audit "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Komponen dan Pengguna tidak dapat diubah setelah pembuatan untuk keamanan "
"dan tujuan audit."

msgid "Connection Health"
msgstr "Kesehatan Koneksi"

msgid ""
"Connection health is automatically updated when you test the connection from "
"the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Kesehatan koneksi akan diperbarui secara otomatis saat Anda menguji koneksi "
"dari wizard."

msgid "Create Provider"
msgstr "Buat Pemroses Pembayaran"

msgid "Please use the Provider Connection Wizard"
msgstr "Silakan gunakan Wizard Koneksi Penyedia"

msgid ""
"For the best experience, please use the <a href=\"/admin/shipping/wizard/"
"step1/\">Provider Connection Wizard</a> to set up new providers."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pengalaman terbaik, silakan gunakan <a href=\"/admin/shipping/wizard/"
"step1/\">Provider Connection Wizard</a> untuk mengatur penyedia baru."

