msgstr "Buka Portal Pengembang FedEx"

msgid "You'll need a valid email address and basic business information."
msgstr "Anda memerlukan alamat email yang valid dan informasi bisnis dasar."

msgid "Create a New Project"
msgstr "Buat Proyek Baru"

msgid "After logging in to your developer account:"
msgstr "Setelah masuk ke akun pengembang Anda:"

msgid "Click 'Create New Project' or navigate to 'My Projects'"
msgstr "Klik 'Buat Proyek Baru' atau navigasi ke 'Proyek Saya'"

msgid ""
"Give your project a descriptive name (e.g., 'My Store Shipping Integration')"
msgstr ""
"Berikan nama deskriptif untuk proyek Anda (misalnya, 'Integrasi Pengiriman "
"Toko Saya')"

msgid "Select the APIs you need (at minimum: Ship, Track, Rates)"
msgstr "Pilih API yang Anda butuhkan (minimal: Ship, Track, Rates)"

msgid "Accept the terms of service"
msgstr "Terima ketentuan layanan"

msgid "Generate API Credentials"
msgstr "Buat Kredensial API"

msgid "In your project dashboard:"
msgstr "Di dashboard proyek Anda:"

msgid "Navigate to 'API Credentials' or 'Keys & Secrets'"
msgstr "Navigasi ke 'Kredensial API' atau 'Kunci & Rahasia'"

msgid "Click 'Generate New Credentials' or 'Create API Key'"
msgstr "Klik 'Buat Kredensial Baru' atau 'Buat API Key'"

msgid "You will receive an API Key (Client ID) and API Secret (Client Secret)"
msgstr "Anda akan menerima API Key (Client ID) dan API Secret (Client Secret)"

msgid "Copy both values immediately - you'll need them in the next step"
msgstr ""
"Salin kedua nilai tersebut segera - Anda membutuhkannya dalam langkah "
"berikutnya"

msgid "Important!"
msgstr "Penting!"

msgid ""
"FedEx will only show your API Secret once. Make sure to save it securely "
"before closing the page."
msgstr ""
"FedEx hanya akan menampilkan API Secret Anda sekali. Pastikan menyimpannya "
"secara aman sebelum menutup halaman."

msgid "Choose Your Environment"
msgstr "Pilih Lingkungan Anda"

msgid "FedEx provides two environments for API integration:"
msgstr "FedEx menyediakan dua lingkungan untuk integrasi API:"

msgid "Test Environment"
msgstr "Lingkungan Uji"

msgid ""
"Use this for development and testing. It allows you to simulate shipments "
"without creating real labels or charges. Recommended for initial setup."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan ini untuk pengembangan dan pengujian. Ini memungkinkan Anda "
"mensimulasikan pengiriman tanpa membuat label atau biaya nyata. Disarankan "
"untuk pengaturan awal."

msgid "Production Environment"
msgstr "Lingkungan Produksi"

msgid ""
"Use this for live shipments with real tracking numbers and charges. Requires "
"account approval from FedEx."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan ini untuk pengiriman langsung dengan nomor pelacakan dan biaya "
"nyata. Memerlukan persetujuan akun dari FedEx."

msgid ""
"Start with the Test environment to verify your integration works correctly "
"before switching to Production."
msgstr ""
"Mulailah dengan lingkungan Test untuk memverifikasi integrasi Anda bekerja "
"dengan benar sebelum beralih ke Production."

msgid "Gather Your Account Information"
msgstr "Kumpulkan Informasi Akun Anda"

msgid "You will also need your FedEx account number. This can be found:"
msgstr "Anda juga memerlukan nomor akun FedEx Anda. Ini dapat ditemukan:"

msgid "On your FedEx invoices"
msgstr "Pada tagihan FedEx Anda"

msgid "In your FedEx account dashboard (fedex.com)"
msgstr "Di dashboard akun FedEx Anda (fedex.com)"

msgid "By contacting FedEx customer service"
msgstr "Dengan menghubungi layanan pelanggan FedEx"

msgid ""
"Your account number is required for generating shipping labels and accessing "
"certain features."
msgstr ""
"Nomor akun Anda diperlukan untuk membuat label pengiriman dan mengakses "
"fitur tertentu."

msgid "Need Help?"
msgstr "Butuh Bantuan?"

msgid "If you encounter any issues during setup:"
msgstr "Jika Anda mengalami masalah selama proses pengaturan:"

msgid "Visit the"
msgstr "Kunjungi"

msgid "FedEx Developer Support"
msgstr "Dukungan Pengembang FedEx"

msgid "for detailed documentation"
msgstr "untuk dokumentasi terperinci"

msgid "Check the"
msgstr "Periksa"

msgid "FedEx API Reference"
msgstr "Referensi API FedEx"

msgid "Contact FedEx Developer Support at"
msgstr "Hubungi Dukungan Pengembang FedEx di"

msgid "Before Proceeding, Make Sure You Have:"
msgstr "Sebelum Melanjutkan, Pastikan Anda Memiliki:"

